cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.RO

The paper deals with visual place recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses supervised hashing, which is a machine learning technique, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely sub-category. The paper deals with image retrieval, which falls under the sub-category of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the efficiency of the proposed method, which is relevant to multimedia systems (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO).
